     H            Y.
      ** GAHR30 *******************************************************
      *  UPDATE OF TRANSPORTATION M/F
      *  KIRI                                            2017.06.28
      *****************************************************************
     FGAHPW30 CF  E                    WORKSTN
      *
      * TRANSPORTATION M/F                         *
     FGAHPL30 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
      *
      * CARRIER M/F  LF1
     FGAHPL35 IF  E           K        DISK
      * ROUTE M/F  LF1
     FGAHPL37 IF  E           K        DISK
      *===============================================================
     E                    ER      1  20 60
      *===============================================================
      *---（時刻）
     I            DS
     I                                        1   40W$TM
     I                                        1   20W$JJ
     I                                        3   40W$FF
     I            DS
     I                                        1  10 D2TRCD
     I                                        1   2 D2CARR
     I                                        3   3 D2HF1
     I                                        4   7 D2ROUT
     I                                        8   8 D2HF2
     I                                        9  10 D2BIN#
     I****************************
      *プログラム状況データ構造*
     I****************************
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W$PGM
     I                                      244 253 W$WSID
     I                                      254 263 W$USER
     I                                      264 269 W$JBNO
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140@TIME
     I                                        1   60@SYSTM
     I                                        7  140@SYSHZ
     C*===============================================================
     C*
     C*===============================================================
     C                     MOVE '#INIT   '@STEP   8
     C*
     C           @STEP     DOUEQ'#END    '
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#INIT   '#INIT            初期処理
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#DSP1   '#DSP1
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#CHK1   '#CHK1
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#DSP2   '#DSP2
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#CHK2   '#CHK2
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#CHK2U  '#CHK2
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#UPDAT  '#UPDAT
     C                     ENDCS
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C*===============================================================
      * 初期ﾈｮmb
     C*===============================================================
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
     C                     MOVEA*ALL'0'   *IN
     C                     TIME           @TIME
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1KKBN           更新区分
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1CARR            CARRIER
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1ROUT            ROUTE
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1BIN#            BIN #
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1ERR            d[ｰxｮﾈｰﾆﾞ
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D2KKBN           更新区分
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D2CARR            CARRIER
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D2ROUT            ROUTE
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D2BIN#            BIN #
      *
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C                     ENDSR
     C*===============================================================
      *画面１*
     C*===============================================================
     C           #DSP1     BEGSR
     C*
     C                     EXFMTGAHPW301
     C                     MOVEA'00000000'*IN,21
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C                     MOVE '#CHK1   '@STEP
      *-------*
      * (F1)  *
      *-------*
     C   KA                MOVE '#END    '@STEP
      *-------*
      * (F20) * CARRIER MASTER
      *-------*
     C           *INKU     IFEQ *ON
     C                     CALL 'GAHC35'
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
      *-------*
      * (F22) * ROUTE MASTER
      *-------*
     C           *INKW     IFEQ *ON
     C                     CALL 'GAHC37'
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
      *-------*
      * (F24) * DOWNLOAD
      *-------*
     C           *INKY     IFEQ *ON
     C                     CALL 'GAHC31'
     C                     MOVE '#END    '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*===============================================================
      *画面１チェック
     C*===============================================================
     C           #CHK1     BEGSR
      *----------------------*
      * UPDATE更新区分
      *----------------------*
S1   C                     SELEC
 1   C           D1KKBN    WHEQ '0'                        :取消
     C                     MOVEL'0-CANCEL'D2KKBN
     C                     SETON                     29    (PR)
 1   C           D1KKBN    WHEQ '1'                        :変更
     C                     MOVEL'1-CHANGE'D2KKBN
     C                     SETOF                     29    (CS)
 1   C           D1KKBN    WHEQ '2'                        :追加
     C                     MOVEL'2-ADD   'D2KKBN
     C                     SETOF                     29    (CS)
 1   C                     OTHER
     C                     SETON                     2199
     C                     MOVELER,1      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
E1   C                     ENDSL
      *----------------------*
      * CARRIER (22)
      *----------------------*
     C           D1CARR    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     2299
     C                     MOVELER,2      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D1CARR    CHAINGAHPL35              91
     C  N91      G5SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           G5SKHZ    ANDLE@SYSHZ
     C                     SETON                     91
     C                     ENDIF
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SETON                     2299
     C                     MOVELER,3      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
      *----------------------*
      * ROUTE   (23)
      *----------------------*
     C           D1ROUT    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     2399
     C                     MOVELER,4      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D1ROUT    CHAINGAHPL37              91
     C  N91      G7SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           G7SKHZ    ANDLE@SYSHZ
     C                     SETON                     91
     C                     ENDIF
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SETON                     2399
     C                     MOVELER,5      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
      *----------------------*
      * BIN #   (24)
      *----------------------*
     C           D1BIN#    IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     2399
     C                     MOVELER,6      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
      *----------------------*
      *----------------------*
      *----------------------*
     C           KEY01     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           D1CARR
     C                     KFLD           D1ROUT
     C                     KFLD           D1BIN#
     C*
     C                     MOVE D1CARR    D2CARR
     C                     MOVE D1ROUT    D2ROUT
     C                     MOVE D1BIN#    D2BIN#
     C                     MOVE '-'       D2HF1
     C                     MOVE '-'       D2HF2
     C*
     C           KEY01     CHAINGAHPL30             N90
      **
S1   C                     SELEC
     C*
-1   C           D1KKBN    WHEQ '0'                        :CANCEL
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SETON                     212223
     C                     SETON                     24  99
     C                     MOVELER,7      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C           G3SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           G3SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     SETON                     212223
     C                     SETON                     24  99
     C                     MOVELER,8      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
-1   C           D1KKBN    WHEQ '1'                        :CHANGE
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SETON                     212223
     C                     SETON                     24  99
     C                     MOVELER,9      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C           G3SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           G3SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     SETON                     212223
     C                     SETON                     24  99
     C                     MOVELER,8      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
-1   C           D1KKBN    WHEQ '2'                        :ADD
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *OFF
     C           G3SKJY    ANDEQ' '
     C                     SETON                     212223
     C                     SETON                     24  99
     C                     MOVELER,10     D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
E1   C                     ENDSL
      *----------------------*
      *----------------------*
     C                     MOVEA'00000000'*IN,31
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2FREQ           FREQUENCY SHIPMENT
     C                     Z-ADD0         D2NSTM           NEW SHIPMENTASTART
     C                     Z-ADD0         D2OSTM           OLD SHIPMENTASTART
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     D2CHDT           CHANGE OVER DATE
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2ERR
S1   C                     SELEC
 1   C           D1KKBN    WHEQ '0'                        :CANCEL
     C                     MOVELG3FREQ    D2FREQ           FREQUENCY SHIPMENT
     C                     Z-ADDG3NSTM    D2NSTM           NEW SHIPMENTASTART
     C                     Z-ADDG3OSTM    D2OSTM           OLD SHIPMENTASTART
     C                     Z-ADDG3CHDT    D2CHDT           CHANGE OVER DATE
 1   C           D1KKBN    WHEQ '1'                        :CHANGE
     C                     MOVELG3FREQ    D2FREQ           FREQUENCY SHIPMENT
     C                     Z-ADDG3NSTM    D2OSTM           OLD SHIPMENTASTART
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     D2CHDT           CHANGE OVER DATE
E1   C                     ENDSL
     C*
      *----------------------*
     C           $CHK1Z    TAG
      *----------------------*
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '#DSP2   '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
      *----------------------*
     C                     ENDSR
      *===============================================================
      *画面２表示
      *===============================================================
     C           #DSP2     BEGSR
     C                     EXFMTGAHPW302
     C                     MOVEA'0'       *IN,99
     C                     MOVEA'00000000'*IN,31
     C                     MOVE '#CHK2   '@STEP
      *----*
      * F3 *
      *----*
     C           *INKC     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SETOF                     202122
     C                     SETOF                         99
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
      *----*
      * F5 *
      *----*
     C           *INKE     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE '#CHK2U  '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDSR
     C*===============================================================
      *画面２チェック
     C*===============================================================
     C           #CHK2     BEGSR
     C*
      *
      *  追加・変更のみチェック
S1   C           D1KKBN    IFEQ '0'                        :CANCEL
     C                     GOTO $CHK2Z
E1   C                     ENDIF
     C*-------------------------
      *  FREQUENCY SHIPMENT
     C           D2FREQ    IFNE '1'                        1=DAILY
     C           D2FREQ    ANDNE'2'                        2=OTHER
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,11     D2ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK2Z
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * SHIPMENT START TIME
     C                     Z-ADDD2NSTM    W$TM
     C                     EXSR ##TIM
     C   99                SETON                     32
     C   99                GOTO $CHK2Z
      *
      *
      * CHANGE OVER DATE
     C           D2CHDT    IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     3699
     C                     MOVELER,14     D2ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK2Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     MOVELD2CHDT    P1DATE
     C                     CALL 'DATR10'
     C                     PARM           P1DATE  8
     C                     PARM           P1RTN   1
     C           P1RTN     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     3699
     C                     MOVELER,15     D2ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK2Z
     C                     ENDIF
      *----------------------*
     C           $CHK2Z    TAG
      *----------------------*
S1   C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C           @STEP     ANDEQ'#CHK2U  '
     C                     MOVE '#UPDAT  '@STEP
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '#DSP2   '@STEP
E1   C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDSR
      *================================================================
      *===============================================================
     C           ##TIM     BEGSR
      *
     C           W$TM      IFNE 9999
      *時刻　時
     C           W$JJ      IFLT 00
     C           W$JJ      ORGT 24
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     ENDIF
      *時刻　分
     C           W$FF      IFLT 00
     C           W$FF      ORGT 60
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C   99                MOVELER,13     D2ERR
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
     C*===============================================================
      *ファイル更新処理
     C*===============================================================
     C           #UPDAT    BEGSR
     C*
     C           KEY01     CHAINGAHPL30              90
     C   90                CLEARGAHPL301
     C*
S1   C                     SELEC
-1   C           D1KKBN    WHEQ '0'                        :CANCEL
     C                     MOVEL'D'       G3SKJY           DELETE CODE D
     C                     Z-ADD@SYSHZ    G3SKHZ           DELETE DATE
     C                     Z-ADD@SYSTM    G3SKTM           DELETE TIME
     C                     MOVELW$USER    G3SKNM           DELETE PERSON
-1   C                     OTHER                           :ADD CHANGE
     C                     MOVEL' '       G3SKJY           DELETE CODE D
     C                     Z-ADD0         G3SKHZ           DELETE DATE
     C                     Z-ADD0         G3SKTM           DELETE TIME
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    G3SKNM           DELETE PERSON
     C                     Z-ADD@SYSHZ    G3KOHZ           UPDATE DATE
     C                     Z-ADD@SYSTM    G3KOTM           UPDATE TIME
     C                     MOVELW$PGM     G3KOPG           UPDATE PROGRAM
     C                     MOVELW$USER    G3KONM           UPDATE PERSON
     C                     MOVELD1CARR    G3CARR           CARRIER
     C                     MOVELD1ROUT    G3ROUT           ROUTE
     C                     Z-ADDD1BIN#    G3BIN#           BIN #
     C                     MOVELD2FREQ    G3FREQ           FREQUENCY SHIPMENT
     C                     Z-ADDD2NSTM    G3NSTM           NEW SIHPMENT START
     C                     Z-ADDD2OSTM    G3OSTM           NEW SIHPMENT START
     C                     Z-ADDD2CHDT    G3CHDT           CHANGE OVER DATE
E1   C                     ENDSL
      *
     C   90                WRITEGAHPL301
     C  N90                UPDATGAHPL301
     C*
     C*
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1KKBN           更新区分
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D1CARR            CARRIER
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D1ROUT            ROUTE
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1BIN#            BIN #
     C                     SETON                     20
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C                     ENDSR
      *================================================================
      *================================================================
**  ERROR
E-01 UPDATE INSTRUCTION <0 1 2>
E-02 INPUT CARRIER CODE
E-03 NOT IN CARRIER MASTER
E-04 INPUT ROUTE CODE
E-05 NOT IN ROUTE MASTER
E-06 INPUT # OF BIN
E-07 THERE ISN'T CANCEL DATA
E-08 DATA IS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-09 NO DATA
E-10 DATA EXIST
E-11 "1"-DAILY  OR  "2"-OTHER
E-12 INPUT TIME
E-13 RANGE IS 00:00 -- 23:59  OR  99:99
E-14 INPUT DATE
E-15 DATE ERROR
E-16
E-17
E-18
E-19
E-20
